                "message":"error",
                "errors":["not found"]
            }

# Group Events
Events related resources. An event has the following attributes:

* Id
* Name (This consists of the event's name and its associated sport)
* Description (Wiki link)
* Sport
* Gold Medalist(s)
* Silver Medalist(s)
* Bronze Medalist(s)

