## /api/event/{eventname}
### Retrieve an event [GET]
+ Parameters

    + eventname (required, string, `alpine_skiing-womens_giant_slalom`) ... Associated sport name followed by the event name separated with "-". Notice how special characters such as " ' " are ignored.
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                    "id": 15,
                    "name": "Women's Giant Slalom",
